location: Academie Duello, 412 Hastings, Vancouver, BC V6B 1L1, CA
description: Our last feature genre dance and we're going big with Brazilian Zouk, and the amazing Shawn Cheng! BZouk is super flowy and connected mixing spirals with body undulations for a unique feeling dance you'll never want to end! Coalescence is a Fusion Social Dance on 1st, 2nd(Masked), 3rd & 5th Sundays. No partner necessary, come dance with everyone! We welcome all dancers, new and experienced from all styles.
